14. h5{ All the minor pieces may have gone, but Black's king is certainly the less comfortable of the two monarchs. White always has  Kb1  if needed and may find expansion through both  c2 - c4  and  f2 - f4  useful. So too, of course, could be doubling the rooks on the  h -file, as we'll see in  Chapter 1B.  }
