13. d4{ A piece sacrifice, but otherwise Black would surely get massacred down the open  h -file. }
14. exf6
14. exf6
15. Ne2{ Plugging the  e -file and simply intending to nudge the rook up to  h2  if Black now captures on  g2 . With  Bf3  and  f2 - f3  also timely possibilities, Black surely doesn't have anything like enough for the piece. }
