12. h6{ Placing a fish bone in the black king's throat, while preventing ... h6  and even allowing White to contemplate ideas of  Bg7 , as well as of  Bc4  and  Qg4 . }
12. f6
13. Bc4+
13. Kh8
14. Qh5{ With the bishop on  e5  immune due to mate, White was doing very well in Gormally-Roy, Helensburgh 2013. }
