15. Rfd8( 15...Qa3+ 16.Kd2 e6 17.Rh3! { Preparing to treble on the open file. }17...c5 18.Qh4 Rfc8 { and White quickly won with }19.Rdh1 { in Hebden-Krakops, Capelle-la-Grande 1995, but }19.Qh7+ { would have somewhat more aesthetic or more brutal, depending on your view. }19...Kf8 20.Qxg7+! Kxg7 21.Bg5 { Black is caught in a classic mating net. } )
