9. Qd2{ A sensible, natural move, facilitating  O-O-O  while keeping  f2 - f3  in reserve. }( { The immediate }9.f3 { has been slightly more popular, but after }9...Nxe5 10.Bxe5 Qb6 { we couldn't find anything amazing for White, which }11.Na4 Qa5+ 12.b4?! Nd7! { certainly isn't. } )
