13. h5{ This is even stronger than recapturing on  g4 , as White did in Darini-Aravindh, Internet (blitz) 2021. }( { While White is now ready to increase the pressure with  Rdg1 , there is already an immediate threat of }13...-- 14.h6 Bh8 15.h7+ { , clearing the  h -file for the attack to crash through. } )
13. gxh5
14. Rdg1( { Black surely isn't going to survive this assault with White ready to go }14...-- 15.fxg4 { and if }15...hxg4 { then }16.Qe1 { followed by  Qh4  will be very powerful indeed. } )
