12. h6
13. Bc4+
13. Kh7
14. Qe2{ Ideas of  e3 - e4  were very much on the table and  a2 - a4  also looked like a useful advance, leaving White with the more compact position, safer king and clear advantage in Stefanova-Bodnaruk, Riadh  (blitz) 2017. }
