5. h4{ We both wondered about this move and were thinking of adding it as a secondary option when Okhotnik's book 'The Modernized Barry Attack' appeared, where he denotes the move as '!N' - high praise indeed. We're not sure that it's quite that strong, but it's certainly worthy of further exploration and should surprise opponents. }( { Now, of course, }5...Bg4 { would just walk straight into }6.Ne5 { . } )
5. Bf5
