4. Bg7
5. Nb5( { The fashionable line of the Barry and one you may wish to consider employing as well as our main recommendation, }5.e3 { .  While a grandmaster is unlikely to be caught out by }5.Nb5 { , it may well have surprise value at lower levels and even cause a few opponents to panic since White does have an immediate threat. } )
