10. Nc3( { A decent square for the knight and now there's a definite positional threat in }10...-- 11.Bxa6 bxa6 12.Na4 { . } )
10. b6{ A very natural choice and one many opponents may plump for, but it is rather slow. }
11. h4{ Upping the ante and seizing the initiative, with  h4 - h5  followed by  O-O-O ,  e3 - e4 ,  Bh6  and mate on the  h -file now White's crude and fairly strong plan. }
11. h5
