12. Nc7
13. O-O-O{ White enjoys promising attacking chances. He may next prepare  g2 - g4  or even make that advance as a dangerous sacrifice. To see how play may develop, do refer back to Le Quang Liem's aforementioned win to which play has now transposed. }
