12. h4
12. h5( { Here, }13.Ng5 { swiftly became a rout in Hebden-Chyzy, Titled Tuesday Blitz 2021, and White had even better: } )
13. g4{ Now simply  gxh5  is very much an issue, as well as such ideas as  e5 - e6  and  Ng5 , all the while as Black's undeveloped state of affairs presents a pretty horrific spectacle. }
13. hxg4
